text: Murtabak or motabbaq () is a kind of pancake. It is filled with ingredients, such as chopped meat and vegetables. It is a street food in Yemen, Indonesia, Malaysia, Thailand, and Singapore. Murtabak was first made by Indians in Yemen. It was brought to Southeast Asia by Indian traders. == References == Category:Indonesian food Category:Malaysian food Category:Singaporean food Category:Thai food Category:Yemeni food
